cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS

The paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The focus is on lifelong learning, which involves a sequence of related tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves optimization and exploration, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), respectively.
